Diagnostics:

  UnusedIncludes: None



CompileFlags:

  Remove:

    - -fno-rtti

    - -fno-exceptions

    - -mthumb-interwork

    - -fno-use-cxa-atexit

    - -fno-threadsafe-statics

    - -Wno-register

    - -Wno-aggregate-return



  Add:

    - --target=arm-none-eabi

    - -mcpu=cortex-m33

    - -mfloat-abi=hard

    - -mfpu=fpv5-sp-d16

    - -D__RA6M5__

    - -D__DCACHE_PRESENT=1

    - -D__ICACHE_PRESENT=1

    - -D__FPU_PRESENT=1

    - -D__DSP_PRESENT=1

    - -DARM_MATH_CM33



---

If:

  PathMatch: .*\.(cpp|cc|cxx|hpp|hh|hxx)$

CompileFlags:

  Add:

    - -std=c++17



---

If:

  PathMatch: .*\.c$

CompileFlags:

  Add:

    - -std=c11